        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Reporting Instances of Non-authorized Grift Act of 2021 or the RING Act of 2021 </strong></p> <p>This bill requires creditors to establish a hotline for assisting consumers who are 50 years of age or older to resolve billing errors and mitigate fraud. </p>]]>
        </text>
